<p>I&#8217;ve been thinking quite a bit about the growth and evolution of my blog recently, and I decided to share with you some of the things I&#8217;ve learned over the last couple of years. Although many of my readers are are regular bloggers themselves, hopefully you will still get something useful out of this, quite long post.</p>
