<p>For Advertisers:</p>
<ul>
<li><span>you want fixed prices month-to-month</span></li>
<li><span>potentially some SEO value - is at the publishers discretion</span></li>
<li><span>you don&#8217;t want long-term commitments</span></li>
<li><span>you want to manage your campaigns from one centralized location instead of dealing with individual publishers </span></li>
<li><span>our network of niche sites is where you will reach your target audience</span></li>
<li><span>our system is incredibly easy to use (set it and forget it)</span></li>
<li><span>we&#8217;re friendly and easy to deal with</span></li>
