<p>This reminds me&#8230; I&#8217;m waiting for my CodeIgniter T-Shirt to arrive since SXSW! <img src='http://www.haughin.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_sad.gif' alt=':(' class='wp-smiley' /></p>
